    LogPrinter

    A System.Action<T> delegate that can be used to redirect the log output. By default the log output will be send to the output window.

    Declaration
    public static Action<TimeSpan> LogPrinter { get; set; }
    Property Value
    Type Description
    System.Action<System.TimeSpan>

    A System.Action<T> delegate which will be invoked to output the elapsed System.TimeSpan. The default delegate will print the output to the output window.
